<h4 id="head-3ce56f72b52e5daf6171d3ddcb0f5a654e4629c9">Combined Spells</h4>
<p>
There is one combined school spell available for the maeta school: 
</p>

    <ol type="4">

    <li>
<p>
<strong>Tracker</strong> (dual school: Meta/Conveyance level 30) Tracks down the last teleportation that happened on the level and teleports you to it. 
</p>
</li>

            <ul>

            <li>
<p>
 Your Meta and <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fConveyance"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Conveyance</a> skills must have reached a combined average level of 30 in order to cast this spell. 
</p>
</li>

            </ul>    </ol>


<h4 id="head-906abc02ff3d872f162af0a481dce9a5c5462baa">God given ability</h4>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fIntroduction_20to_20the_20Gods_20of_20ToME#head-5bd0243a84a97d0e2433360b77f003d1eaa40eb8"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Manwe Sulimo</a> at 1/3 prayer level. 
</p>
</li>
</ul>

